The Peter Schiff Show
Wednesday, 21 March 2012


[sebaygo1]


Today's first guest is Sen. John Hoeven, junior senator from North Dakota, on how horribly Obama's signature achievement has already destroyed America's health care industry.

Today's second guest is Sen. Rand Paul, junior senator from Kentucky, on the Illinois primary results, rumors of deal between his dad and Romney, and Rep. Paul Ryan's budget.
